briefly speaking, git is to back-up or record history versions of a project.

types of version control system:
local version control system.  Problem: cannot develop collaboratively
centralized version control system(short for 'CVCS'), such as Cvs, Subversion, Perforce. Problem: single point of failure
distributed version control system(short for 'DVCS'), such as Git, Mercurial, Bazzar, Darcs

Git最早是在linux上开发的，两者作者都为Linus Benedict Torvalds
windows download page：https://git-scm.com/download/win
initial config：git config --global user.name "your user_name"
                git config --global user.email xxx@xx.com
                git config --list (see all the configs)
                git --version(see the version of git)
            
